name: Elizabeth Leibi
description: Oh, isn’t it a difficult task to describe oneself character, especially for a lady? My mood is always good, because I am very optimistic. It can be strange, but yes – you can be sure I am a person who smiles all the time and do not even think about bad things. So, that is my type! To open my soul, if you look inside, you can see a very kind girl with a mild character. I am very real and sometimes it brings me much harm, but that is life. I have a very positive attitude to everything and if I am here – it means I am lucky to have a chance to meet you.
